{"id": 4731, "title": "Ticket #4731: RPM installs and condor_config.local", "description": "<blockquote>\nIn version 8.2.4, the packaged installs (RPM and deb) no longer include a /etc/condor/condor_config.local. If this file has been customized, it will be moved to an .rpmsave file during an upgrade. So, customizations within this fill are not read.\n\n<p>We will have to preserve these customizations.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2014-Nov-20 15:20:56 by edquist:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>code review</strong>\n\n<p>TimT's new changes to condor.spec/condor.spec.in look good to me.  I have tested this in OSG with the unified rpm and everything works as expected -- a modified condor_config.local stays in place after the update with a README.condor_config.local dropped in, and an unmodified one just cleanly disappears.</p></blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-Nov-24 15:51</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=41753\">[41753]</a></span>: minor 8.2.5 version history item edit <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"defer\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=4731\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4731'); return false;\" title=\"RPM installs and condor_config.local\">#4731</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-Nov-20 16:59</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=41728\">[41728]</a></span>: Version history for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"defer\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=4731\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4731'); return false;\" title=